column2: comedy2018.plot <- ggplot(comedy2018, aes(x = likesratio, y = dislikesratio, text = paste("Likes: ",likes))) + geom_point(aes(size = views, col = channel_title), show.legend = F) + labs(x = "Likes Ratio", y = "Dislikes Ratio", title = "Likes vs Dislikes in Trending Comedy Videos 2018") + theme_algoritma + theme(legend.position = "none")
